-- ALTER VIEW univmed.fato_universo_medico
-- AS
SELECT
[KEY_CRM]
,[CICLO]
,[KEY_CRM_EMAIL]
,[UF]
,[CRM]
,[CRM2]
,[EMAIL_PRINCIPAL]
,[EMAIL_SECUNDARIO]
,[NOME]
,[ESPECIALIDADE]
,[ESPECIALIDADE2]
,[ESPECIALIDADE3]
,[VISITADO]
,[NETWORK_ID]
,[VEEVA_ID]
,[RX_GIGYA_ID]
,[TELEFONE]
,[CELULAR]
,[EMAIL]
,[EMAIL_ORIGEM]
,[ONE_MASS]
,[ONE_ONE]
,[VISITADO_GSK]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Universo Medico/dimensao_universo_medico_*.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH (
[KEY_CRM]				  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CICLO]				  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_CRM_EMAIL]		  VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[UF]					  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CRM]					  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CRM2]					  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[EMAIL_PRINCIPAL]		  VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[EMAIL_SECUNDARIO]		  VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[NOME]					  VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ESPECIALIDADE]		  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ESPECIALIDADE2]		  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ESPECIALIDADE3]		  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[VISITADO]				  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[NETWORK_ID]			  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[VEEVA_ID]				  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[RX_GIGYA_ID]			  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TELEFONE]				  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CELULAR]				  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[EMAIL]				  VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[EMAIL_ORIGEM]			  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ONE_MASS]				  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ONE_ONE]				  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[VISITADO_GSK]			  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
    ) AS ROW
